item.title: About Us
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
A True Premium Theme

ThemePunch has dedicated a lot of time and ressources to create a new kind of Wordpress Theme that is highly creative, unique, technologically advanced, yet still highly customizable and easy to use by beginners and developers alike.

We highly suggest that you take a look at all the features this product has to offer, including all different previews so you can grasp the full potential of GoodWeb. We are very proud of this product and are anxious to see what sites you will build using it!

Sincerely, your Team @ Themepunch

Special Fullscreen Slider
Our "2-Layer Fullscreen Image Slider" system allows you to optionally show 2 separate images. The first image is shown on top of the page when no content is present. Once the user scrolls down, the second image fades in, allowing for blurred backgrounds, alternate views, tiled backgrounds, etc. Your creativity is the limiting factor here!
Timeline Style Blog
Our timeline style blog provides a modern and readable way of presenting your post content. Its possible to chose from a variety of different layouts with or without excerpts, images and media.
Real Filterable Portoflio
Our custom made filterable portfolio has 2 - 6 grid layout options with selectable item heights. The real kicker though is the fact that the filtering works throughout all pages of your whole portfolio!
Light & Dark Skins
GoodWeb comes with 2 premade skins (light & dark) to suit your personal taste!
Visual Content Builder
The visual content builder used in goodweb allows for content editing in a live view! Changing a text or adding an element will directly be visible, as seen on the final page, in the editor window.
WPML Support & More
GoodWeb of course includes a range of the most popular ThemePunch plugins (Slider Revolution, ShowBiz Pro) and offers support for popular plugins like WPML (multilanguage), Contact Form 7, etc.

Client Testimonials

[rev_slider testimonialslider]
  • One Pager
  • Multi Pager
  • Mixed
GoodWeb has the ability to show multiple pages / modules on one page, essentially forming a "one-pager". The menu icon in the top-left will always show the page you have currently scrolled to. By clicking the icon and opening the menu, you can also directly jump to a specific point on the page.
You can also use GoodWeb like any regular WordPress theme with separate single pages that can be reached via the left main navigation. This flexibility makes GoodWeb a true multipurpose theme that is suitable for creative sites, classic businesses and anything else you can think of.
In addition to the one- and multi-pager functionalities, the GoodWeb theme can also be used as both at the same time (what you are seeing in this preview). You can have a one-pager and still include static links to single pages in the menu!
